    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2006-05-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2006-06-09T17:27:11Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Trade Readjustment Allowances for Adversely Affected Workers Act of 2006 - Amends the Trade Act of 1974 to treat any week in which employment is unavailable to an adversely affected worker because of a lockout as a week of employment. (Thus, counts such weeks for purposes of qualifying such a worker for a trade readjustment allowance.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Trade Readjustment Allowances for Adversely Affected Workers Act of 2006</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
